LibriSync - Audible Library Sync for Mobile
Copyright (C) 2025 Henning Berge
Project URL: https://librisync.henning.tech

================================================================================

This software is a Rust port of Libation, an Audible audiobook manager and
DRM removal tool. The Rust implementation is a derivative work that maintains
the architecture, data models, and business logic of the original C# codebase.

Original Work: Libation
Copyright: Libation contributors
License: GNU General Public License v3.0
Repository: https://github.com/rmcrackan/Libation

================================================================================

ATTRIBUTION NOTICE

This project is a systematic translation of Libation's C# source code to Rust,
preserving the original implementation details while adapting to Rust idioms
and mobile platforms (iOS and Android).

Component Mapping:
- native/rust-core/src/api/       ← Libation's AudibleUtilities/
- native/rust-core/src/crypto/    ← Libation's AaxDecrypter/ + Widevine/
- native/rust-core/src/storage/   ← Libation's DataLayer/
- native/rust-core/src/download/  ← Libation's FileLiberator/
- native/rust-core/src/audio/     ← Libation's FileLiberator/
- native/rust-core/src/file/      ← Libation's FileManager/

Each Rust module contains detailed comments referencing the corresponding C#
source files and line numbers from the original Libation implementation.

